---
import ball from "../assets/ball-water.jpg";
import court from "../assets/red-clay-court.jpg";
---

<div
	id="content"
	class="bg-gray-200 flex flex-col items-center text-base-content py-30"
>
	<div class="container mx-auto">
		<div class="flex flex-col gap-16">
			<div
				class="flex flex-row items-center justify-between bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl"
			>
				<div class="flex-1 max-w-xl">
					<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-5">Rich Tennis Heritage</h2>
					<p class="mb-5 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
						The original character and unique charm of the club has been
						preserved over the years. The  club’s courts have  been used by
						national teams in preparation for tournaments worldwide. Affiliated
						to Tennis Ireland it hosts many significant competitions throughout
						the year including the Munster National Tour 500 Clay Court
						Championships and the Munster Masters Tour 1000 Claycourt
						Championships.
					</p>
				</div>
				<img
					class="w-4/12 rounded-2xl drop-shadow-2xl hidden md:inline mx-8"
					src={ball.src}
					alt="Tennis ball spinning in the air with water droplets flying off"
				/>
			</div>

			<div
				class="flex flex-row items-center justify-between bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl"
			>
				<img
					class="hidden md:inline mx-8 w-4/12 rounded-2xl drop-shadow-2xl"
					src={court.src}
					alt="Clay tennis court with white lines"
				/>
				<div class="flex-1 max-w-xl text-left">
					<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-5">A Rare Clay Court Experience</h2>
					<p class="mb-5 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
						We offer 3 exceptional clay courts maintained to offer the perfect
						playing conditions. We provide a welcoming environment to inspire
						the passion of the game and uphold the tradition and integrity of
						this sport.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
